 	<li style="font-weight: 400;">Survey Gizmo:<strong><a href="https://www.surveygizmo.com/survey-blog/how-to-develop-a-market-research-plan/" target="_blank"> Como desenvolver um plano de pesquisa de mercado</a></strong></li>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;">Entrepreneur:<strong><a href="https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/241080" target="_blank"> As melhores maneiras de fazer pesquisas de mercado para seu plano de negócios</a></strong></li>
 	<li style="font-weight: 400;">Business.com: <strong><a href="http://www.business.com/market-research/creating-a-market-research-plan/" target="_blank">Como criar um plano de pesquisa de mercado </a></strong></li>
</ul>
